plot: Just when it seems things can't get worse, Batwoman's identity is once again at risk of being exposed; some of Gotham's most villainous unite; Sophie joins Luke on a mission; Alice gets into Mary's head.

While Marquis pays a visit to Arkham and gets some new recruits, Victor Zsasz come after Jada as she has a reunion with Ryan. Mary and Alice look for Joker's old toymaker to repair the buzzer that she made for the villain. Batwing and Sophie break into Wayne Tower to find incriminating evidence on Marquis.—Gislef
